---
title: Soy-Marinated Pork with Crunchy Potato, Sugar Snap Peas and Carrot Medley
description: Crunchy sugar snap peas and crispy creamy potatoes peppered with carrots and mint? This fresh side is paired with a soy-marinated pork to make the ultimate weeknight dinner.
